yed the battle full well.  Her little hole beneath the ground sucking up it's victims.  Where Elektra could shred them before they could scream.  She loved it.  Bathing in her victim's blood.  The would be assassin was pure predator.  But down in her whole, she saw nothing of what happened above.  Til the screams and sounds of weapons were finally stilled, Elektra then came out of her fox hole.  Her dark armour shimmering in Roman blood, Elektra followed her sisters from far behind.  <br>
