 &quot;I know.&quot; She replied simply. &quot;You have proven your valor, Alysia and I know you will continue to do so.&quot; She smiled softly at her.<br>
 As they arrived at the encampment, Marpe helped Solari off her horse and began to prepare the daggers as Solari had requested. Solari made her way, slowly to the shelter she had been in earlier and sat back down on the furs. Her mind raced thru the plans she was forming, and of the pain that seeped in her veins. She reached into her bag nearby as she waited on the hot daggers to sear her wounds with, and pulled out a small vile with some liquid in it. She watched as the other amazons came into the encampment with looks of defeat on their faces. She needed to reassure them that things would be ok.<br>
 Marpe brought the red hot daggers to her and Solari removed her shirt and pants, removing the blood-soaked bandages. She pulled the cork out of the small vile, drinking down the liquid and then taking one of the daggers and plunging it into her leg. The pain from the heat sent a shock thru her body, causing Solari to wince as a result. She could ignore that pain, but knew that her side would be another matter. She grabbed a piece of leather and placed it in her mouth before reaching for the other dagger. She loked at Marpe, who had a look of concern on her face, then looked down at her wound, sliding the dagger in. The smell of burnt flesh filled her nostrils as Solari bit down on the leather strap, muffling her cry of pain. She pulled the dagger out, then collasped back, trying hard to hide the tears that were now flowing from her eyes.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=daughterofshylock>Daughter of Shylock</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.picturesof.net/_wallpaper/rose_Dsc08151_WP.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 269<br> <font color=#993300>(4/5/03 10:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=140>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.picturesof.net/_wallpaper/rose_Dsc08151_WP.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Planning Begins</span><hr size=1> Alysia walked around the camp as she watched the other amazons and their feel of defeat. She even overheard two younger ones speaking.<br>
