&quot;Words like that should be considered treason! Hippolyte would give her life for you, if you died today you would have died with honor.&quot; She growled and walked into a sheltered area of the woods where she sat down. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">~*~ Jessica ~*~<br>
